      <biogHist id="md5-37af863e988870079dde188391c3f9fb">
        <p>The Athletic Association was organized as a department under the Students' Union to encourage amateur athletic sports and physical culture among the students.  Its main executive dealt with activities for the men students; a parallel Women's Athletic Association developed.  After 1946 the two were amalgamated into the University Athletic Board.</p>
